---
title: One-Pot Pork Pilaf with Yoghurt & Crushed Peanuts
description: One-pot cooking isn’t just convenient, it’s also full of lots of lovely flavours as everything comes together. Take this delicious pork veggie pilaf, the chermoula spices melt in the bowl. One irresistible and easy dinner coming right up!
